Finding the image gallery a bit cumbersome to use, but on the other hand being too lazy to create a new one from scratch, I decided to use &lt;a href=&quot;http://vikjavev.no/highslide/&quot;&gt;Highslide JS&lt;/a&gt;. This nice piece of JavaScript software really adds a new dimension to the gallery, making it easier to use and looking great at the same time. It also makes the page feel more - no matter how much I hate the term - Web 2.0.&lt;/p&gt;
